{"tid":1087470,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"廣東話教你畫水彩玫瑰花","createTime":"2019-04-01T11:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T18:04:33.000Z","uid":75427,"like":150,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"22faecef5f7c4a6a52061eedefd823b247d891a8","tid":1087470,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"連仔居然真係開咗藝術台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教學方面歡迎提出意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有唔明都可以問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單歸納要點：<br />\n1.  中間深色外面淺色<br />\n2. 花瓣大小中間細外面大<br />\n3. 花瓣一塊疊一塊，圍圈圈<br />\n4. 花瓣形狀呈彎月形，三角形等<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VWBf99PpUUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVWBf99PpUUA&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQiy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=25f6a889\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VWBf99PpUUA</a>"},{"pid":"9eb2b2d8d1cbfe743af7bc6b25b8d32ee9f2852a","tid":1087470,"uid":75427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:54:22.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"bd07c9cbf74f1d7a29cc70eb327ed6fc0d4b4567","tid":1087470,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:56:35.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"39d7a19f9d7c90eaf5ed0e97a25f99f9230e5360","tid":1087470,"uid":75427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fr